What&apos;s New in Piece_Unity_Component_Authentication 1.1.0

 * includes/excludes: Two configuration points &quot;includes&quot; and &quot;excludes&quot; have been added. &quot;includes&quot; allows you to mark multiple URIs as protected resources by regexp. This configuration point behave same as &quot;resourcesMatch&quot;. &quot;excludes&quot; allows you to mark multiple URIs as non-protected resources by regexp. And also the authentication URI has always been excluded from the protected resources.</notes>
  </release>
